Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.70,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:そうなのよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:二段レシーブ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.03,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{NOTE:この場で実験してみよう。}
